N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 13 ยง 94.1 - Availability of forms and instructions

State Regulations

Forms and instructions for registration and filing may be downloaded from the

Attorney General's website at www.oag.state.ny.us/charities/charities.html or by writing to New York State Attorney General, Charities Bureau, 28

Liberty Street, New York, NY 10005 or at any other website or address designated by the Attorney General. Notes
